            Data-Driven <span class="text-primary">Copywriting</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Data-driven content and copywriting examples featuring comprehensive research, statistical analysis, and proven results in SEO content strategy and conversion optimization.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/" class="border border-primary text-primary py-3 px-8 rounded-lg font-orbitron font-bold hover:bg-primary hover:text-black transition-all duration-300 inline-block">
              ← Back to Portfolio
